  • Type Parameters:
    S - The type of the TableView generic type (TableView<S>)

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget, javafx.scene.control.Skinnable

    public class InjectedComboBoxTableCell<S,T>
extends javafx.scene.control.cell.ComboBoxTableCell<S,T>
    A ComboBoxTableCell that uses a custom defined ComboBox.

    If you just want to use a default ComboBox but call some mutators on the ComboBox, use MutableComboBoxTableCell instead.

    Provided ComboBox will have its OnAction and OnKeyReleased set to those as used by the default ComboBoxTableCell.
